  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] pmfs are used to represent the statistics of the stochastic streams associated with edges in the Tanner graph. However, the variable node update involves recalculating probabilities, and sampling takes up to steps and requires computing or updating a cumulative density function.",
